summary.span: 提供接聽項，將所有追蹤和偵錯輸出路由至 IIS 7.0 基礎結構。

span.span: Provides a listener that routes all tracing and debugging output to the IIS 7.0 infrastructure.

remarks.format: ## Remarks 類別會連接的追蹤機制[!INCLUDE[vstecasp](~/includes/vstecasp-md.md)]至[!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)]。The class connects the tracing mechanism of [!INCLUDE[vstecasp](~/includes/vstecasp-md.md)] to [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)]. 這個接聽程式類別可讓開發人員建立[!INCLUDE[vstecasp](~/includes/vstecasp-md.md)]應用程式和人員實作並介面來引發事件的頁面層級、 模組層級或處理常式層級以[!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)]追蹤時的基礎結構已啟用。This listener class enables developers who create [!INCLUDE[vstecasp](~/includes/vstecasp-md.md)] applications and who implement the and interfaces to raise page-level, module-level, or handler-level events to the [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)] infrastructure when tracing is enabled. > [!NOTE] > 這個接聽程式的類別不會路由[!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)]ASP.NET 類別的事件。This listener class does not route [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)] events to ASP.NET classes. 這包括類別和類別可實作或介面。This includes the class and classes that implement the or interface. 中導入[!INCLUDE[net_v35_long](~/includes/net-v35-long-md.md)]。 is introduced in the [!INCLUDE[net_v35_long](~/includes/net-v35-long-md.md)]. 如需詳細資訊，請參閱[版本和相依性](~/docs/framework/migration-guide/versions-and-dependencies.md)。For more information, see [Versions and Dependencies](~/docs/framework/migration-guide/versions-and-dependencies.md).
